---
title: Crispy Sunchoke Salad with Kale, Farro and Goat Cheese
description: May is National Salad Month, and have we got something special here. If you've never tried sunchokes, hold onto your hat. Crispy, nutty sunchokes are a root vegetable native to eastern North America, and this salad's pièce de résistance!
